social_posts.post_text: Happy New Year friends! Stayed up till 4 am finishing off my first book of 2023! I was not expecting the ending so I’ll warn you, grab some Kleenex. Now onto the next! Hope your first week of the new year is off to a good start! 🥳♥️
How is January gone already? Been busy working on things over here. My website is also down 😂 but I’ll have things up and running soon! Happy February friends! ♥️
New stickers slowly rolling out 😄 used my kid as a hand model cuz my hands are so dry from this cold weather 😭 who’s ready for spring?
So simple.🤍
Got to work on these custom cutie portraits last year. It was probably my favourite project. I’ll be adding them to Etsy soon for your own teams! ♥️⚾️♥️ #oba

The world is a small, small place. It reminds me to be kind to the people around you because you never know who’s going to end up in your life down the road. 📸 by @adie8 who ordered this six years ago and now we’re mamas on the same baseball team! 🖤

Last of the Christmas in July orders going out today! Thank you everyone for your patience! I got in trouble from Etsy, for dispatching two days later 🙄 I forgot how much I dislike them as a platform. Ah well. Sometimes life happens you know? Like your son injures himself doing his favourite thing in the whole wide world. But on a happy note! ITS FRIDAY!!! 😁 Happy weekend pals! 💖

ITS HERE! 🎄 website will be live tomorrow for all your ornament needs. I am weeding some styles out but if you still want those, please message me and let me know what you’re looking for. I’m always happy to help! Not all ornaments will be available on Etsy this year. Local pick up is always available! And I’ll still be adding things as the holidays approach, I’m just putting it out there early so I can get ahead of the madness! ♥️
Website is live! If you see any mistakes please let me know! My eyes started blurring after a while 😅 and the coffee was not helping. Happy Friday friends! ♥️
Christmas things still slowly coming 🥰🎅🏼

Got to make these and then Canada Post lost them! And then I started remaking them… and then Canada Post found them 😆 thanks for all your patience Michelle! ⁣
⁣
Side note: see that @cityandcolour_official portrait in the back? It was gift from my wedding photographer and it’s my fav! And he’s coming to OSHAWA!!!! Who’s going!? 🙋‍♀️🙋‍♀️🙋‍♀️
Sometimes I work on something and I don’t know if it looks right, so I leave it. I’ve had this card in my work in progress for 2 years. I think it’s ok? 🤷‍♀️ Christmas cards up in the shop!
Pack, pack, packing. 💕
Can I tell you how much work these cards were? My hands cramped for days. My arthritis flared up. But here they are! 😍 Cards and Holiday mats are up!
I’m ready for a sprinkling of light snow. You know the kind, that just floats by looking pretty but doesn’t accumulate. But first I gotta rake up all these dang leaves. Happy Monday friends!
Process. Sometimes it takes forever. Sometimes it doesn’t. But mostly it does 🤭🎄☃️
Black and white. Always a classic 🖤

Slowly building up Christmas over here. Can I just say, I love this dang tv. When my  husband first brought it home it was like “I thought you went out to pick up pho?” Which he also came back with… but changing the wallpaper every season is my favourite ♥️ Happy Friday friends!

Sawyer 🐶♥️

Pet ornaments now available but only for a limited time cuz they take a little longer.
Stacks of cards going out! Our Dachshund and Happy Christmas are currently the most popular 🥰 thanks for all the love guys! ♥️🎄

Basically. It’s a PA DAY over here, the kids are home. We had waffles for breakfast and by the time I was done cleaning the kitchen, it was lunch time already 😭 putting on the Christmas music and finishing up the week! Happy Friday friends! 🎄♥️

It’s giving warm and fuzzies when a home town store stocks up on your stuff 🥰 Christmas cards are now available at @isabellaschocolatecafe in downtown Oshawa ♥️🎄♥️ Grab a treat, a warm drink on this freezing day and say hi to Rosanna for me! 

📍2 King Street East.

Pack an ornament with me! Tbh I dunno what I’m doing 🫢 I didn’t even know how to use my kids phone holder thingy. But I love wrapping ornaments! Because I hope that you love opening them! ♥️ side note: Taylor Swift sounds good at any speed 😝🥰

As Black Friday and the end of our season approaches, I wanted to remind you that we offer local pickup! If you’re in the Durham Region area and want to save on shipping you can choose Local Pickup on our website and I’ll shoot you a message when your order is ready! Or you could use code HOMETOWNGLORY on Etsy and it will waive the shipping fee. ♥️🎄
All pending ornaments going out tonight! I’m really digging the matte colours. The ink just pops on them ♥️

HAPPY FRIDAY!!! I know you’re all probably busy getting ready to hit up the malls. But just wanted to post that everything on our website is discounted 20% until Monday! Discount is available on www.paperfelt.ca currently not via Etsy. 

If you have any questions, DM me or email me… but if I don’t get back to you today it’s cuz I’m still looking for those coveted Uggs for my kid 🙄🫠 wish me luck!

Happy Monday friends! It’s lightly snowing over here, the coffee is warm and I’m ready to start all these orders ♥️ Thank you guys for keeping me busy! 😊 otherwise I’d still be here over decorating the house and singing Christmas carols to the dog 🫢 

Today is the last day of our sale! ♥️🎄♥️ and we no longer have mint, pink and rose! But we do have a lot of other pretty colours!

How many trees do you have in your house? We have 2. One that looks pretty and the real one with all our memories and those ugly kids crafts made with pipe cleaners and popsicles sticks that will one day make me cry when the kids are grown. 

But one pretty tree for this lady, who managed to make her kids crafts look nice while throwing a mix of my ornaments in there ♥️ // video by @itonille

Local orders ready for pickup! And lots more going out but please bear with me. Canada Post is having technical difficulties 😬 Happy December friends! 🎄♥️🎄 PLEASE NOTE! This is the last weekend to order ornaments! It takes about a week to fulfill so I want to make sure you have them in time for Christmas!
All the white glass in our shop! These are the most popular colours always. Iridescent is no longer available. 🎄

LAST CALL! Today will be your last day to order for expected on time deliver before Christmas. Please note, we will get your order out on time but once Canada Post has it… I mean they’re usually pretty good. So I have high hopes. Local and provincial people still have time! December 17 is the cut off for you:) 

Lots of orders going out today. If you ordered last week your order will be out by end of week. ♥️
Happy snow day GTA friends! Staying cozy today and wrapping up the rest of your orders! 🎄♥️ also new packaging for flat ornaments! 🥰 Although I will miss the cotton bags.

Anyone else? How is it less than two weeks till Christmas? My house is a mess. My kids have all these activities. I have to see people I don’t wanna see 🤣 Happy holiday season everyone! 🎄♥️ may we all survive.
Working on the last order of the year! It’s a pick up so I’m not stressed. And then I’m cleaning the house cuz this season got me in a mess of packaging, tape and glitter. Happy Friday friends! 🎄♥️

GIVEAWAY! I know it’s close to Christmas and you probably won’t get these in time but at least you can store them for next year! Giving away ONE custom name ornament, your choice of colour and if it’s a first year or not. Or if you want a saying on it… that’s cool too! 

TO ENTER: Like this post, follow and tag a buddy. Maybe they’ll win one too 😉 Because it’s so close to Christmas, this giveaway runs for one day only. Ends tomorrow at midnight and then I’ll raffle, ink it out and ship it off as quickly as I can! Shipping is only to Canada and USA. 

Happy last week before Christmas! 🎄♥️🎄
Round one of teacher gifts 😂 Honestly, I have like 8 teachers over here. But I love them all so… here’s to the ones that need a drink. The rockstars, the admin team 🤘♥️

Still on holiday mode over here! Just finished reading this one, it was… cute. It would have been better without all the intimate scenes, Melody was cool all on her own. But also especially awkward when your kids are running around playing and then ask you what’s happening in your book right now 😆😳 still a cute premise. ⭐️⭐️
